<ul>
  <li> serve as liaison to the Secretary and Deputy Secretary of HHS; </li>
  <li> review all existing and proposed HHS regulations and legislation; </li>
  <li> promote OIG activities and accomplishments by reaching out to the public, media and other external entities; </li>
  	
				
